@Mistobaan Mostly a rebase but there are a couple Go specific changes. The exported TF_DataType, and TF_Codes enums needed to be declared differently, also there was a type mismatch where Swig needed a long long instead of an int64_t.

I'd be happy to rebase/squash locally and resubmit for a cleaner PR.

body:
@Mistobaan Mostly a rebase but there are a couple Go specific changes. The exported TF_DataType, and TF_Codes enums needed to be declared differently, also there was a type mismatch where Swig needed a `long long` instead of an `int64_t`.

I'd be happy to rebase/squash locally and resubmit for a cleaner PR.
